Scarcely a wine-lover in America needs an introduction to Mr. Alexis Lichine—one of the great and renowned wine experts of the world. Six bottles of his own elegant, delicate Chateau Prieuré- Lichine 1971 and six bottles of the illustrious, rich Chateau Lascombes 1971 cradled in our popular James Beard Wine Rack will make an especially fine gift for anyone who loves the great wines of the Haut-Medoc. Both of these top-flight grands crus from the famed commune Margaux will pro- vide years of dramatic wine-drinking pleasure.
